sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CM as Conversation Manager
    participant Router as Intent Router
    participant AgentA as Agent A<br/>(Job Agent)
    participant AgentB as Agent B<br/>(Query Agent)
    
    User->>CM: "Find expensive queries in job 123"
    
    Note over CM,Router: Step 1: Classify Intent
    CM->>Router: classify_intent()
    Router-->>CM: Route to JobAgent
    
    Note over CM,AgentA: Step 2: Process with Agent A
    CM->>AgentA: Process job analysis
    AgentA->>AgentA: Analyze job, identify queries
    AgentA-->>CM: Partial results + handoff request
    
    Note over CM,AgentB: Step 3: Handoff to Agent B
    CM->>AgentB: Continue with query analysis
    AgentB->>AgentB: Analyze queries, generate recommendations
    AgentB-->>CM: Final results
    
    Note over CM,User: Step 4: Return Combined Results
    CM-->>User: Combined output<br/>(Job + Query Analysis)
    
    Note over User: Seamless experience<br/>despite agent handoff

